WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: zh-Hant

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:06.000
&lt;i&gt;Fasten seatbelt sign ON&lt;/i&gt;

00:01:05.779 --> 00:01:09.735
女士們、先生們，
我們的飛機馬上就要著陸

00:01:09.735 --> 00:01:13.761
請您再次確認繫好您的安全帶，
謝謝。

00:01:13.870 --> 00:01:18.252
Ladies and gentlemen, our
plane will be landing shortly.

00:01:18.337 --> 00:01:23.605
Please confirm that your seatbelt
is securely fasten, thank you.

00:04:57.082 --> 00:05:04.637
女士們、先生們，
我們已經到達北京首都機場。

00:05:04.825 --> 00:05:07.732
您將在三號候機樓升降。

00:05:07.732 --> 00:05:13.506
機艙外的溫度：
4 攝氏度 ；39 華氏度

00:05:13.694 --> 00:05:16.290
飛機還將滑行一段距離，

00:05:16.290 --> 00:05:20.837
請您繫好您的安全帶，
在座位上耐心等候。

00:05:20.837 --> 00:05:23.857
直到安全帶指示燈熄滅。

00:05:23.857 --> 00:05:27.150
在此期間，請不要打開手機。

00:05:27.451 --> 00:05:32.957
下機時，請小心開啟行李箱，
以免行李滑落。

00:05:33.204 --> 00:05:39.078
感謝您選乘星空聯盟成員—
中國國際航空公司的航班。

00:05:39.078 --> 00:05:42.498
我們期待與您下次旅途再會。

00:05:39.078 --> 00:05:46.052
祝您在北京愉快，再見。

00:05:48.973 --> 00:05:52.652
Ladies and gentlemen, 
we have just landed 

00:05:52.652 --> 00:05:57.326
at Beijing Capital 
International Airport, Terminal 3.

00:05:57.307 --> 00:06:01.631
The temperature is 4 degree Centigrade

00:06:01.632 --> 00:06:04.476
or 39 degree Fahrenheit

00:06:04.553 --> 00:06:08.162
Please remain seated with your 
seatbelt fastened 

00:06:08.163 --> 00:06:09.924
and the luaggages stored

00:06:10.238 --> 00:06:13.622
The use of mobile phone
is prohibited 

00:06:13.623 --> 00:06:16.852
until the seatbelt sign has 
been switched off.

00:06:17.109 --> 00:06:20.121
And we'd remind you 
to your precaution

00:06:20.122 --> 00:06:22.543
when opening the 
overhead compartment.

00:06:22.831 --> 00:06:25.923
Please take all your belongings 
with you

00:06:25.924 --> 00:06:27.547
when you disembark.

00:06:27.703 --> 00:06:30.803
Thank you for flying with 
Air China,

00:06:30.804 --> 00:06:33.215
a member of Star Alliance.

00:06:33.393 --> 00:06:37.103
And we hope you'll enjoy
your stay in Beijing,

00:06:37.104 --> 00:06:38.998
thank you and good-bye!

